import jax
import jax.numpy as jnp

def generated_fn(x0):
    v0 = jnp.sin(x0)
    v1 = jnp.cos(v0)
    v2 = jnp.minimum(x0, x0)
    v3 = jnp.add(v1, v0)
    v4 = jnp.subtract(x0, v1)
    v5 = jnp.add(v1, v3)
    v6 = jnp.minimum(v0, v4)
    v7 = jnp.maximum(v0, v5)
    v8 = jnp.multiply(v7, v5)
    return v8
